ComicInfo.Title: The Twilight of SOME Gods!
ComicInfo.Summary: The Twilight of SOME Gods!: The Eye of Odin tells Thor of how the current group of Asgardian Gods was created after the previous set experienced their own Ragnarok. The Ragnarok burned Asgard to brightly that it became the star that was followed by the three wise men in the Bible.
